BCam v2
--------

Requirements:
- Xilinx ISE (14.4 recommended)
- ZTEX SDK (FWLoader, FX2 libraries)
- lm32-gcc toolchain
- FPGA board udev rule for your user

Synthesize:
- Open BananaCam2_ufm.xise in Xilinx ISE
- Click on Toplevel file (BC2_top_ufm.v)
- "Synthesize - XST"
- Get a coffee

Transfer to FPGA board:
- % make prog

Clean up:
- In Xilinx ISE: Project -> Cleanup Project Files -> Ok
